### Ports (application)

{{#if persistsToDynamo}}
- `{{pascal featureName}}Repository` — `findById`, `save`, plus access patterns required.
{{/if}}
{{#if publishesEvent}}
- `EventPublisher` — `publish(event: DomainEvent): Promise<void>`.
{{/if}}

### Adapters (infrastructure)

{{#if persistsToDynamo}}
- `Dynamo{{pascal featureName}}Repository` — implements port using `@aws-sdk/lib-dynamodb` `DynamoDBDocumentClient`. Single-table design; PK/SK strategy defined in companion `platform-dynamodb-table` spec.
{{/if}}
{{#if publishesEvent}}
- `EventBridgeEventPublisher` — implements `EventPublisher` using `@aws-sdk/client-eventbridge`. Batches up to 10 entries per `PutEvents` call.
{{/if}}

## API contract

- **Endpoint**: `{{httpMethod}} {{resourcePath}}`
{{#if authRequired}}
- **Auth**: `Authorization: Bearer <jwt>`. APIGW authorizer validates and injects `requestContext.authorizer.claims`.
{{/if}}
- **Request schema**: `src/infrastructure/handlers/schemas/{{kebab featureName}}.request.schema.json`
- **Response schema**: `src/infrastructure/handlers/schemas/{{kebab featureName}}.response.schema.json`
- **Status codes**: 200/201 on success, 400/401/404/409/500 per error mapping.

